	quest.48FFEB9924643C86.quest_desc: [
		"&lBees in Nests&r - Those bees will live only in nests, so you can't use them for honey, but breed them with various bees to get new species."
		""
		"&lLure bees to Nests&r - Some bees can work in hives but to get them you have to lure them by finding or creating special Nests and inserting their favorite breed. Or put Hives into darkness and wait a night to capture ZomBee or Skeletal Bee."
		""
		"&lCombining Bees&r - Breed some various Bees to get new species."
		""
		"&lConverting Bees&r - Feed a vanilla Bee with TNT to convert it to CreeBee, etc."
		""
		"&lQuarry Bee&r and &lWoodcutter Bee&r can collect various rocks or woods."
		""
		"&lFarmer Bee&r - just flying around and breaking harvestable items, and &lCollector Bee&r is collecting  them."
	]
